I would strongly recommend either using FillPixelArray (as Mark already 
proposed), use EraseRect, or not use the ScrollVPort trick at all. This is 
only considered a historic feature because early V3 cybergraphics has trouble 
with it, and the W3D_SetDrawRegion call was added because with two bitmaps 
you cannot use EraseRect without a temp rastport. 

